iewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check size-4 text-green-500 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg><span class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Gratis 2 bulan</span></li><li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check size-4 text-green-500 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg><span class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Akses Pro Penuh</span></li><li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check size-4 text-green-500 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg><span class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Unlimited Project</span></li><li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check size-4 text-green-500 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg><span class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Unlimited Photos</span></li><li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check size-4 text-green-500 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg><span class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Prioritas Support</span></li></ul></div><div data-slot="card-footer" class="flex items-center px-6 [.border-t]:pt-6"><a href="https://ryaneko.myr.id/m/fastpik-pro-access" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" data-slot="button" data-variant="default" data-size="default" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap rounded-md text-sm font-medium transition-all disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg:not([class*=&#x27;size-&#x27;])]:size-4 shrink-0 [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 outline-none focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-ring/50 focus-visible:ring-[3px] aria-invalid:ring-destructive/20 dark:aria-invalid:ring-destructive/40 aria-invalid:border-destructive bg-primary text-primary-foreground hover:bg-primary/90 h-9 px-4 py-2 has-[&gt;svg]:px-3 w-full cursor-pointer">Pilih Paket</a></div></div></div><div class="mt-16 text-center"><p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">Pembayaran diproses dengan aman oleh Mayar.id.<br/>Hanya mendukung QRIS.</p><p class="mx-auto mt-3 max-w-2xl text-xs text-muted-foreground">Bisa untuk pembelian baru atau perpanjangan. Jika langganan masih aktif, durasi paket baru akan ditambahkan ke tanggal berakhir saat ini. Gunakan email yang sama dengan akun Fastpik agar perpanjangan masuk ke akun yang benar.</p></div></main><footer class="py-6 border-t text-center text-sm text-muted-foreground"><p>Made with ❤️ from <a href="https://instagram.com/ryanekopram" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:underline">@ryanekopram</a> &amp; <a href="https://instagram.com/ryanekoapps" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:underline">@ryanekoapps</a></p></footer></div><!--$--><!--/$--><script src="/_next/static/chunks/538c6f1fdc57b776.js" id="_R_" async=""></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"1:\"$Sreact.fragment\"\n2:I[39756,[\"/_next/static/chunks/ff1a16fafef87110.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/650b0d2d0b895b93.js\"],\"default\"]\n3:I[37457,[\"/_next/static/